 <span class="gramGrp"><span class="xr"> <a class="link-right verbtable" href="https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/spanish-english/conjugation/creer">Verb Table</a> </span><span class=" hi rend-sc pos">transitive verb</span></span>
 <div class="sense">
  <span class=" sensenum bluebold">1.&nbsp;</span> 
  <span class="lbl type-syn"><span class=" punctuation">(</span><span class=" punctuation">=&nbsp;</span>considerar cierto<span class=" punctuation">)</span></span> 
  <span class="cit type-translation quote">to believe</span>
  <div class="cit type-example">
   <span class="quote">nadie me cree</span> 
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">nobody believes me</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cit type-example">
   <span class="quote">créame</span> 
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">believe me</span>
   <span class=" bluebold"> ⧫ </span>
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">take my word for it</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cit type-example">
   <span class="quote">no creo lo que dijo</span> 
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">I don’t believe what she said</span>
  </div>
  <div class="re type-phr">
   <span class="form type-phr orth">¡ya lo creo!</span>
   <span class=" punctuation">: </span>
  </div>
  <div class="cit type-example">
   <span class="quote">—¿quieres un café? —¡ya lo creo!</span> 
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">“do you want some coffee?” — “you bet!”<span class="lbl type-register"> <span class=" punctuation">(</span>informal<span class=" punctuation">)</span></span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="cit type-example">
   <span class="quote">¡ya lo creo que está roto!</span> 
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">you bet it’s broken!</span>
   <span class=" bluebold"> ⧫ </span>
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">it certainly is broken!</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cit type-example">
   <span class="quote">¿que yo voy a ir andando hasta el faro? ¡ya lo creo!</span>
   <span class="lbl type-register"> <span class=" punctuation">(</span>ironic<span class=" punctuation">)</span></span> 
   <span class="cit type-translation quote">you think I’m going to walk all the way to the lighthouse? you must be joking!<span class="lbl type-register"> <span class=" punctuation">(</span>informal<span class=" punctuation">)</span></span></span>
  </div>
